▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒
▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀
*/      
Static Function ZGPR01_011()
Local cCodFunc		:= ""		//-- codigo da Funcao do funcionario
Local cDescFunc		:= ""		//-- Descricao da Funcao do Funcionario
Local cDepto        := ""       
Local nTc			:= 0		//-- T. C. 
Local dData         := "00/00/00"

/*
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Carrega Funcao do Funcion. de acordo com a Dt Referencia     │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘*/
fBuscaFunc(dDataRef, @cCodFunc, @cDescFunc)   
 
//calcula o ultimo dia do mes do Periodo selecionado para buscar o campo nTc
dData:=  F_UltDia(dDataRef)     
dData:= DaySum( dDataRef , dData-Day(dDataRef) )
nTc := fTabela( "S009", 1, 5, dData)
 
//carrega departamento                                            
cDepto:= fDesc("CTT", SRA->RA_CC, "CTT->CTT_DESC01", 30)

@ ++LI,00 PSAY "*"+REPLICATE("=",130)+"*"
                                                    
LI++
@ LI,00  PSAY "|"
@ LI,02  PSAY Alltrim(Desc_Fil)
@ LI,113 PSAY "FECHA: " + DTOC(date())
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"

LI++            
@ LI,00  PSAY "|" 
@ LI,115 PSAY "HORA: " + time()
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"

@ ++LI,00  PSAY  "|"
@ LI,58  PSAY "BOLETA DE PAGO"
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"

@ ++LI,00  PSAY  "|"  
@ LI,02  PSAY Alltrim(Desc_Cid) + "- BOLIVIA"
@ LI,57  PSAY "PLANILLA MENSUAL"		//"PLANILLA MENSUAL"
@ LI,115 PSAY MesExtenso(Month(dDataRef)) + "/" + left(DTOS(dDataRef),4)
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"

@ ++LI,00  PSAY  "|" 
@ LI,100 PSAY "T.C.:" + Transform(nTc, "99.99999") 		//T.C.: 
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"

@ ++LI,00 PSAY "|"+REPLICATE("-",130)+"|"

@ ++LI,00 PSAY "| " + "Nome:" + SRA->RA_NOME
@ LI,61 PSAY "C.I.C.: " + SRA->RA_CIC 
@ LI,103 PSAY "Admissõo:" + DTOC(SRA->RA_ADMISSA)
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"
                  
@ ++LI,00 PSAY "| " + "Cargo:" + cDescFunc
@ LI,61  PSAY "CėDIGO: " + SRA->RA_MAT

If cPaisLoc == "BOL"
	@ LI,105 PSAY "Seguro S.: " + SRA->RA_SEGUROS 
EndIf

@ LI,131 PSAY "|"
 
@ ++LI,00 PSAY "| " + "DPTO.: " + cDepto 
@ LI,61 PSAY "H. EXTRAS: " + cValtoChar(nHraExtra)
@ LI,105 PSAY "DIAS: " + "30.00"
@ LI,131 PSAY "|" 

@ ++LI,00 PSAY "| " + "Horas Domingo Trabajado: " + cValtoChar(nPagoDom)
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"
LI ++
@ LI,00 PSAY "|"+REPLICATE("-",130)+"|"

LI ++
@ LI,00 PSAY "|"
@ LI,027 PSAY " I N G R E S O S "		//" I N G R E S O S "
@ LI,090 PSAY "  E G R E S O S"		//"  E G R E S O S"
@ LI,131 PSAY "|"

LI++
nPagoDom	:= 0
nHraExtra	:= 0
Return Nil


