▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀
*/
Static Function  ZGPR01_021(cString,nTipoRel)

If LastKey() = 27 .Or. nLastKey = 27
	Return  .F.
Endif

If nTipoRel == 1 .OR. nTipoRel == 2
	SetDefault(aReturn,cString)
Endif

If LastKey() = 27 .OR. nLastKey = 27
	Return .F.
Endif

Return .T.

